OL,3,CIllegal drugs in staff locker at
OL,4,CUniversity Hospital in Wales, review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe hospital has apologised to staff
OL,8,Fand patients and said this review was
OL,9,Fpart of their efforts to proactively
OL,10,Faddress the issues raised by staff.
OL,12,FThe health board carried out 30,000
OL,13,Fsurgeries in the last year, with over
OL,14,Fa third of those being carried out in
OL,15,Fthe theatres the report focusses on.
OL,17,FChief executive Suzanne Rankin said
OL,18,Fthe service review involved more than
OL,19,Fa third of theatres staff sharing
OL,20,Ftheir views and experiences.
