OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"It uncovered a number of concerning
OL,8,Fthemes, ranging from failures of
OL,9,Fleadership practice, variable
OL,10,Fcompliance with policies and
OL,11,Fprocedures and poor culture, all of
OL,12,Fwhich impact upon behaviours and
OL,13,Fpsychological safety of colleagues,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
