OL,3,CIllegal drugs in staff locker at
OL,4,CUniversity Hospital in Wales, review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"The health board will now consider
OL,8,Fthe findings, recommended actions and
OL,9,Fimplications of the service review as
OL,10,Fit develops a management response and
OL,11,Fa detailed action plan to make urgent
OL,12,Fimprovements and address quality and
OL,13,Fsafety issues.
OL,15,F"While very disappointing and
OL,16,Fconcerning, the health board conducts
OL,17,Fmore than 30,000 surgical procedures
OL,18,Fin Cardiff and the Vale of Glamorgan
OL,19,Fevery year and the number of incidents
OL,20,Faffecting patients is proportionately
OL,21,Fvery small.
