OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"However, this does not diminish the
OL,8,Fresponsibility we hold to ensure we
OL,9,Fseek continuous improvement, and we
OL,10,Fwant to assure the public that safety
OL,11,Fmeasures remain a top priority for the
OL,12,Fhealth board.
OL,14,F"We are very sorry for the distress
OL,15,Fand concern this will cause, and we
OL,16,Fwant to reassure the public that we
OL,17,Fwill take the necessary steps to
OL,18,Faddress the concerns raised."
