OL,3,CIllegal drugs in staff locker at
OL,4,CUniversity Hospital in Wales, review
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe Executive Medical Director for the
OL,8,Fboard, Dr David Fluck, said patient
OL,9,Fsafety is the number one priority, and
OL,10,Fdescribed the report as a "challenging
OL,11,Fread".
OL,13,FHe apologised to staff and said: "we
OL,14,Fneed to work out how to tackle this
OL,15,Fand work with the team going forward:
OL,17,F"...It's on us now to keep the staff
OL,18,Fwith us, to keep the staff engaging
OL,19,Fwith us, and we plan and co-produce
OL,20,Fwhat we need to do going forward."
